headline: Adjust Launches Growth Copilot Beta For Smarter, Faster App Growth
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, May 27, 2025--Leading measurement and analytics company Adjust announced today the beta launch of Adjust Growth Copilot, a first-of-its-kind app growth partner. Adjust’s new product, built with client feedback, brings AI directly to modern marketers. With Adjust Growth Copilot, marketers instantly access performance insights across channels, campaigns, and KPIs — helping them optimize strategies and boost revenue.
